Rename to .env
Only keep the last four lines. 
Do not version this file. 
Change parameters as you like. 

Documentation: 
MONGODB_URI - copy-paste the link (including your admin password) from the mongodb website
PORT - well
BUFFER_SYNC_INTERVAL - time in minutes before sheets are backuped to the db (they are always backed up once the last user closes their tab)
CLEANUP_DAYS - remove sheets not accessed after so many days
DEFAULT_FILE - File to fetch for new sheets (offline only, online is always default.json)


MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/headfirst
PORT=443
BUFFER_SYNC_INTERVAL=5
CLEANUP_DAYS=700
DEFAULT_FILE=default.json